Class FoldInAnimation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.androidanimator.animation.Animation
      • com.androidanimator.animation.FoldInAnimation

  • public class FoldInAnimation
extends Animation
    This animation folds in the view for a customizable number of folds, orientation and at a customizable anchor factor.
